        {
            "title": "美銀策略師認為黃金與中國股票成為AI熱潮下的最佳對沖工具",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/w.K1W4DrspRsaglG8FSYfg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/39fcd60d19b3c557fdf1ada09657d549\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美銀策略師指出，面對人工智能板塊的熱潮推高估值，中國股票和黃金是最佳對沖工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500指數遠期本益比達23倍，遠高於過去二十年16倍的平均水平。科技七巨頭占據該基準指數權重的三分之一以上。該類股估值更高，遠期本益比達31倍。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由Michael Hartnett領導的美銀團隊在報告中表示，「AI板塊的領漲態勢短期內不會改變，我們認為黃金和中國股票是應對熱潮/泡沫的最佳對沖工具。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JaJbiuwFGfp6roLqMCN4NQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/06d5c4613275575421ee0595f3251571\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在科技巨頭的帶領下，標普500指數自從4月初低點反彈以來，市值已飆升17萬億美元。位於這場AI浪潮中心的晶片巨頭輝達，本周更是成為全球首家市值達5萬億美元的公司。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5a26803a-4868-3df5-964f-c3cb49b2aeba-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美銀策略師指出，投資者正在為2026年強勁經濟成長佈局投資組合，預期美國利率下行且總統川普將出台支持市場的政策。黃金則為對沖寬鬆政策與經濟擴張可能推升通膨的風險提供了避險工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金近期從每盎司4300美元以上的歷史高位回落，部分原因是投資者評估中美達成貿易休戰以緩解貿易緊張局勢的進展。美銀策略師引述EPFR數據指出，全球黃金基金資金流出量在最新周度數據中達到創紀錄的75億美元，此前已連續四個月出現資金流入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，今年中國股市大幅跑贏標普500指數，在DeepSeek崛起後因市場看好該地區在生成式人工智能領域的競爭力，MSCI中國指數飆升33%。近期這波漲勢有所降溫，隨著部分關注點重新轉向中美長期緊張關係及經濟面臨的挑戰，該指數即將終結連續五個月的上漲勢頭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hartnett及其團隊在川普當選時準確押注亞洲和歐洲等國際股市，預見到這些地區的寬鬆政策將推動股價上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BofA’s Hartnett Sees Gold, China Stocks as Best AI Boom Hedges</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%90%E7%82%BAai%E7%86%B1%E6%BD%AE%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-153422923.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-01 00:15:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股早盤上揚 亞馬遜亮眼業績和蘋果的強勁預期提振風險偏好",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J6erpIgaWnhVtAwhEGXGJA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fd9670ccccc3c98305634f34dd27c55c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受亞馬遜公司的亮眼業績以及蘋果公司強勁的假日季預期提振風險偏好影響，美國股市周五上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至紐約時間上午9:44，標普500指數上漲0.5%。該基準指數自4月份低點以來飆升近40%，邁向連續第六個月走高。以科技股為主的那斯達克100指數周五上漲1%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞馬遜股價飆升，因其雲業務錄得近三年來最強勁的增速。蘋果在發布新款iPhone後預計假日季銷售將出現跳升，這有助於讓投資者相信其旗艦產品仍是成長引擎。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d8da473d-0e75-37c1-9e1f-a5b26546aa3e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7tveINNX8y.Fu6jk85iLEA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/309f1d34fbbf07f8dc84c580de141971\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貿易方面的積極進展也提振了投資者信心。美國總統唐納德·川普在與中國國家主席習近平會面後稱，美中已在中國稀土供應問題上「解決」了分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管關稅談判和科技企業財報傳遞樂觀信號，但在聯儲會本周早些時候對進一步降息的前景表示保留、且由於政府停擺美國進入數據空白期之後，投資者仍面臨前景不明的經濟環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">堪薩斯城聯儲行長Jeff Schmid表示，他在本周對降息投下反對票的原因是擔心經濟成長和投資會對通膨構成上行壓力。達拉斯聯邦儲備銀行行長Lorie Logan也表示，她不支持聯儲會本周降息的決定，並且由於通膨仍然過高，她很可能認為在下次會議上維持利率不變是合適的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題S&amp;P 500 Jumps as Strong Amazon, Apple Scorecards Reignite Rally</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julien Ponthus、Bernard Goyder、Neil Campling.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A9%E7%9B%A4%E4%B8%8A%E6%8F%9A-%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E4%BA%AE%E7%9C%BC%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E5%92%8C%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%81%8F%E5%A5%BD-142448308.html",
